hacking-beacon-plant-start = You start planting the beacon...
hacking-beacon-plant-success = You successfully plant the beacon.
hacking-beacon-unstick-start = You start removing the beacon...
hacking-beacon-unstick-success = You successfully remove the beacon.

hacking-beacon-already-hacked = The beacon refuses to attach itself. This machine has already been hacked.

hacking-beacon-planted-examined = The beacon's display states that it has been planted for [color=red]{$time}[/color] seconds.
